  <summary>5/3/2005--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from the gross income of an employee covered under a high deductible health care plan a distribution from such employee's qualified retirement plan to fund a health savings account. Exempts such a distribution from the 10 percent penalty on early distributions from qualified retirement plans.</summary>
